256432/10-years-taiwans-sunflower-movement-has-wilted-its-legacy-lingers?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>美国议员敦促制裁支持23条国家安全法的香港官员</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3256456/us-lawmakers-urge-sanctions-against-hong-kong-officials-behind-article-23-national-security-law?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>有影响力的国会人物也在考虑加快立法，剥夺该市驻美国贸易办事处的特权。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 21:35:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3256456/us-lawmakers-urge-sanctions-against-hong-kong-officials-behind-article-23-national-security-law?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>随着人工智能战争的升温，苹果正在考虑与中国科技巨头和竞争对手结盟</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3256455/apple-considering-alliances-chinese-tech-giant-and-rivals-ai-war-heats?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>据《华尔街日报》报道，苹果正在与百度洽谈将人工智能引入中国的 iPhone。在中国，人工智能技术——苹果最大的国际市场——必须接受监管机构的审查。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 21:06:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3256455/apple-considering-alliances-chinese-tech-giant-and-rivals-ai-war-heats?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>台湾同意允许免税进口巴拉圭猪肉，中国大陆受挫</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3256454/taiwan-agrees-allow-duty-free-imports-paraguayan-pork-setback-mainland-china?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>“值得庆祝的时刻”被誉为南美国家生产商的福音，这些生产商在因乌克兰战争而对俄罗斯实施制裁后面临着需求疲软的局面。</description><pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 19:55:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3256454/taiwan-agrees-allow-duty-free-imports-paraguayan-pork-setback-mainland-china?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>为什么中国在联合国最高法院的言论可能表明对巴勒斯坦事业的更强有力的支持</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3256382/why-chinas-words-top-un-court-could-signal-stronger-support-palestinian-cause?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国外交官在国际法院的评论似乎支持针对以色列的武装斗争，分析人士称这是“意料之外的立场转变”，但其他人否认这标志着彻底的背离，并指出北京仍然支持两国解决方